  <text xml:lang="ta">
    <body>
      <div xml:id="Aink87-kilavi">
        <p type="edition">talaimakaḷ taṉṉaip puṟaṅkūṟiṉāḷ eṉak kēṭṭa kātaṟparattai avaṭkup
          pāṅkāyiṉār kēṭpat talaimakaṉōṭu pulantu colliyatu.
        </p>
        <p type="translation" xml:lang="en"> </p>
      </div>
      <div xml:id="Aink87">
        <lg type="edition">
          <l>pakaṉṟaik kaṇṇip pallāṉ kōvalar</l>
          <l>karumpu kuṇilā māṅkaṉi yutirkkum</l>
          <l>yāṇa rūraniṉ maṉaiyōḷ</l>
          <l>yāraiyum pulakku memmaimaṟ ṟevaṉō.</l>
        </lg>
        <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">

          <l> O man from a fertile village</l>
          <l rend="indent2"> where cowherds in Jalap chaplets with many cows</l>
          <l rend="indent2"> use sugarcanes as drum sticks to bring down ripe mango fruits! </l>
          <l> Your wife will get in a mood with anyone</l>
          <l> [But] why with us? </l>


        </lg>
      </div>
    </body>
  </text>
